@startuml
title Opportunity – State Machine

[*] --> New
New --> Scored : fusion snapshot created
Scored --> Previewed : user/API Preview
Previewed --> Executed : Risk OK + Exec placed
Previewed --> Blocked : Risk Fail (exposure/cooldown/quality)
Scored --> Expired : t > expires_at
Blocked --> Expired : cooldown elapsed (no re-preview)
Executed --> Completed : fill + journal
Executed --> Failed : reject/timeout

state Executed {
  [*] --> Placed
  Placed --> Filled : tx confirmed
  Placed --> Rejected : venue error
}

note right of Blocked
- reason_code
- policy_id
- until (cooldown)
end note

note bottom of Executed
decision_id, txid, order_json,
post-trade PnL hooks
end note
@enduml
